{"id": "aos005", "name": "Cam_Academy_694_08_01", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["School_Bell", "Class Bell"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma... Congratulations on your discharge from the hospital! Are you feeling alright?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... Thank you. I'm feeling fine.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "We've all heard about it from sis Helena. Everyone here will try their best to help you recover your memory. Do you remember anything about me and the things here?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... No...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "... Is that so...\nNo worries. I'll reintroduce myself then. I'm Clara, the class representative of J-1. If you have any questions, feel free to ask me.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "You really don't remember anything...? You two were really close friends.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Yes... I'm sorry.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "You don't have to apologize... We can build a new friendship starting today! If we're being honest, the person that's real~ close to you is right there~ Iris, why don't you come and greet Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "Ah, she ran away.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate B"], "content": "She said that if Aroma doesn't recognize her, she might just collapse on the spot.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Nah, isn't that a bit overreacting? My grandmother used to have light dementia as well. She recovered after our relatives started spending more time with her. I'll go get her.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "What kind of terrible metaphor is that...? Then I guess I'll go first! Aroma, do you remember me? I'm Thomas; we were dating each other before!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate B"], "content": "Hey! Stopping spewing nonsense. Aroma, don't listen to him. I'm your real boyfri...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Shut your pie holes! Seriously, why are you guys so immature!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos0501"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Waah! You don't have to drag me here...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "What are you talking about? You're Aroma's best friend! If you're not here, what's the point? Maybe seeing you can help her remember something.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "This is Iris. She was your closest friend. Anything comes to mind?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris... Iris...\nIris... Baker...?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "EH!? Do you remember me!?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... Ummm...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "How is it!? Is there anything else you remember!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "... I'm sorry. All I can remember is your last name...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "... <i>*Cries*</i>!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate B"], "content": "Why are you crying? This is good news! Give us some time and we can help her remember everything for sure!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "I know... I know... <i>*Cries*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Jeez, stop crying... Can't tell if you're happy or sad with your face like this.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris... I will try my best.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Yes... <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "Oh, speaking of people that might collapse if forgotten, there's that guy as well... He should be able to help Aroma remember some things.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate B"], "content": "You have a point. He, Clara and Aroma; putting the Big 3 in our class together will certainly help... Ah, but he's probably smoking on the roof again.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "... Should I go get him?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate B"], "content": "Forget about it. Didn't you see him in class? He is in a terrible mood today. He might beat you up if you go talk to him right now.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmate A"], "content": "Sighs~ Seriously, what's the point of having good test scores if you're going to act like that? If he keeps doing this, his conduct score will be in the negatives very soon.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "...... Ah, whatever~ Forget it. Let's take Aroma on a tour of the Academy. Pretty sure that'll be more helpful than waiting here for that punk.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["School_Bell", "チャイム"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……退院おめでとう！具合は大丈夫？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……ありがとう。大丈夫。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helenaさんから話は聞いてるから！\nみんなでAromaの記憶が戻るように手伝うからね！\n私のこと分かる？アカデミーについては？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……分からない……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……そっか……\n気にしないで！じゃあ、自己紹介するね。\n私はClara。J - 1の学級委員長なの。\n分からないことがあれば、何でも聞いてね。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "本当に覚えてないのかよ……？\n前はあんなに仲良かったのに。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん……ごめんなさい。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "謝らないでいいよ……\n今日からまたやりなおそ！\nそれに、本当に仲が良かった子はあっち！\nIris！おいでよ！Aromaと話さなくていいの？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "あーあ、逃げちゃった。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト B"], "content": "Aromaが自分のこと覚えてなかったら、耐えられないって言ってたよ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "もう！そんなに深刻にならなくていいのに！\nうちのおばあちゃんも、前ちょっとボケてきちゃってたけど、家族と過ごしてるうちによくなったし。\nちょっと追いかけてくる！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "ばあちゃんと比較されても……？\nじゃあ、俺からね！\n俺Thomas！俺たち付き合ってるんだぜ！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "え……？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト B"], "content": "おい！何とんでもないウソ吹き込んでるんだよ！\nAromaの彼氏は俺……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "邪魔！男子って本当ガキ！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos0501"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "きゃあ！引っ張らないで……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aromaの親友のあんたがいなくてどうするの！\nもしかしたら、何か思い出すかもしれないでしょ。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "どう？この子はIris。あなたの親友。\n何か思い出せる？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……Iris……\nIris……Baker……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "え！？おっ覚えてるの！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……あ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "どうだ！？何か思い出したか！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……ごめんなさい。苗字しか思い出せない……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……っ……ぅうう……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト B"], "content": "何泣いてんだよ！よかったじゃん！\nもっと頑張れば、絶対全部思い出せるって！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "分かってる……うう……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "ちょっとぉ…泣かないで……嬉しいのか悲しいのか分かんないよ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……私、頑張るね。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "うん…うん……！…うっ…ぅう……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "そういえば、忘れられたら死ぬほどショック受けるやつがもう一人いるな……\nそいつもAromaが記憶を取り戻すために、色々協力してくれるはずだよ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト B"], "content": "だな。あいつとClara、Aroma3人の模範生が一緒にいれば、絶対何か思い出すきっかけができるよ。\n……あ～、でもあいつ今頃屋上でコッソリたばこ吸ってんだろうな。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……呼んでくる？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト B"], "content": "いや、放っておこうぜ。\nあいつ今日機嫌悪いし、殴られたらたまんねぇもん。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイト A"], "content": "ハァ…あいつ成績がどれだけ良くても、あのまんまじゃ素行ポイント全部なくなっちまうよ。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "………？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……もう！あいつのことは放っておけばいいの！\nAromaにアカデミーを案内してあげる方がよっぽど有意義だよ。\nAroma！行こ！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["School_Bell", "課鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……恭喜妳出院！身體還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……謝謝，還好。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我們有聽 Helena 姐說了，大家會努力幫妳恢復記憶的，對我和這邊的事情有印象嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒有……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……是嗎……\n沒關係，我重新自我介紹好了。我是 Clara，是 J - 1 的班長，有不懂的地方都可以問我喔。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "真的不記得了喔……？妳們以前關係很好耶。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "不用道歉啦……從今天開始重新來就好啦！真正關係好的在那邊呢～Iris，不過來關心一下 Aroma 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "啊，跑掉了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "她說要是 Aroma 認不出她，她可能會崩潰。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "哎呀～哪有那麼誇張？我外婆之前也有點老人癡呆，後來家裡人多陪陪她就沒事啦。我去追她。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "什麼爛譬喻啊……？那我先好了！Aroma，還記得我嗎？我是 Thomas，我們正在交往喔！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "咦……？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "喂！你少在那唬爛。Aroma 我才是妳男朋……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "閃開啦！你們這些臭男生！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos0501"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "哇！不要拉我……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "跟 Aroma 最好的妳不在了還怎麼辦？搞不好能幫她想起什麼耶。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "如何？她是 Iris 喔，妳最好的閨蜜，有印象嗎？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……Iris……\nIris……Baker……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "咦！？妳記得我！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……呃……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "怎麼樣！？有想到什麼嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……對不起，只想得起姓而已……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……嗚嗚！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "哭什麼啊？太好了啊！再努力一點我們一定可以幫她想起全部的事情的！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "我知道……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喂喂，別哭了……搞不懂妳是在開心還是傷心。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……我會努力的。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "對了，說到被遺忘可能會崩潰的傢伙，還有一個呢……他應該也能幫 Aroma 想起一些事。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "對吼，他跟 Clara、Aroma 三大模範生聚在一起一定有幫助……啊，不過他現在八成又在屋頂偷抽煙。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……我去叫他？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "算了啦，他今天心情那麼差，搞不好會被揍喔？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "唉，成績那麼好有什麼屁用？他再這樣下去操行遲早會被系統扣光。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……哎呀～別管他了啦，我們帶 Aroma 去參觀學院還比較有用。Aroma，走吧！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["School_Bell", "수업 종"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……퇴원 축하해! 몸은 괜찮아?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……응, 괜찮아. 고마워.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helena 언니한테 다 들었어. 모두들 네 기억을 회복시키려고 엄청 노력했다던데. 나랑 이곳에서 있었던 일도 혹시 기억이 안 나니?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……응……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……그렇구나……\n괜찮아! 그럼 다시 내 소개를 할게. 나는 Clara라고 해. J - 1반의 반장이야. 모르는 거 있으면 언제든지 나한테 물어봐.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "진짜로 기억을 잃어버린 거야……? 너희 둘, 꽤 친했잖아.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응……미안해.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "뭘 사과하고 그래……오늘부터 다시 잘 지내면 되지! 가장 친했던 친구가 저기 있네~ Iris! \nAroma 랑 인사 안 해?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "헉, 그냥 가버렸어.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생B"], "content": "예전에 Aroma가 자기를 못 알아보면 자기는 바로 멘붕올 것 같다고 말한 적이 있었어.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "에휴~ 뭘 그렇게 심각하게 생각하고 그래! 우리 외할머니도 예전에 치매에 걸리셨는데, 가족들이 다 함께 관심 갖고 열심히 챙겨줘서 그런 지 별일 없이 잘 지냈다고! 내가 따라가 볼게!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "무슨 비교가 그래…？좋아, 그럼 내가 먼저! Aroma, 나 기억해? 내 이름은 Thomas! 우린 사귀고 있던 사이라고!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "어....?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생B"], "content": "야! 뭔 헛소리야! \nAroma, 나야말로 예전 네 남자친구였던...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "저리들 안 가!? 하여간 사내 놈들 정말!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos0501"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "아얏! 그만 잡아당겨...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma랑 가장 친했던 네가 여기 있으면 어떡해? 네가 곁에 있으면 기억이 돌아올지도 모르잖아?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "어때? 저 아이는 Iris, 너와 가장 친했던 친구야. 혹시 뭔가 생각나는 거라도 있니?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……Iris……\nIris……Baker……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "앗! 날 기억하는 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……아……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "뭐야 뭐야! 뭐라도 생각난 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……미안해... 이름의 성만 기억났을 뿐이야……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……흐흑!!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생B"], "content": "뭘 울고 그래! 정말 잘 됐다. 우리가 조금만 노력하면 Aroma의 기억도 전부 돌아올 거야!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "알았어…… 흐흐흑……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "야, 야~ 울지 말라니깐.... 지금 기뻐하는 건지 슬퍼하는 건지...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……나, 노력해 볼게...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "응......... 흑... 흐흑....\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "아 맞다! 자기를 기억 못 해서 멘붕 온 녀석이 한 명 더 있잖아.... 걔도 Aroma가 기억을 회복하는데 도움을 줄 수 있지 않을까?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생B"], "content": "맞아! 걔랑 Clara, Aroma, 이렇게 우리 아카데미 3대 간판 모범생들이 함께 모여있으면 분명 기억을 회복하는데 영향을 줄 수 있을 거야..... 아, 그런데 걘 담배 때문에 옥상에서 거의 살다시피 하잖아.....\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……가서 불러올까?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생B"], "content": "됐어. 오늘 기분도 엄청 안 좋아 보이던데, 괜히 얻어 터질수도 있잖아.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생A"], "content": "에휴, 성적이 좋다고 다 능사는 아니야! 걔 계속 이러다간 품행 평가에서 점수 엄청 깎일 텐데.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……에휴～걘 그냥 신경 쓰지 말자. 우리가 Aroma를 데리고 아카데미를 견학시켜 주는 것이 훨씬 더 나은 방법일 수도 있어. Aroma, 가자!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["School_Bell", "課鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……恭喜妳出院！身體還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……謝謝，還好。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我們有聽 Helena 姐說了，大家會努力幫妳恢復記憶的，對我和這邊的事情有印象嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……沒有……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……是嗎……\n沒關係，我重新自我介紹好了。我是 Clara，是 J - 1 的班長，有不懂的地方都可以問我喔。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "真的不記得了喔……？妳們以前關係很好耶。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "不用道歉啦……從今天開始重新來就好啦！真正關係好的在那邊呢～Iris，不過來關心一下 Aroma 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "convers