力的。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "對了，說到被遺忘可能會崩潰的傢伙，還有一個呢……他應該也能幫 Aroma 想起一些事。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "對吼，他跟 Clara、Aroma 三大模範生聚在一起一定有幫助……啊，不過他現在八成又在屋頂偷抽煙。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……我去叫他？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 B"], "content": "算了啦，他今天心情那麼差，搞不好會被揍喔？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學 A"], "content": "唉，成績那麼好有什麼屁用？他再這樣下去操行遲早會被系統扣光。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……哎呀～別管他了啦，我們帶 Aroma 去參觀學院還比較有用。Aroma，走吧！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["School_Bell", "课铃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma……恭喜妳出院！身体还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……谢谢，还好。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我们有听 Helena 姐说了，大家会努力帮妳恢复记忆的，对我和这边的事情有印象吗？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……没有……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……是吗……\n没关系，我重新自我介绍好了。我是 Clara，是 J - 1 的班长，有不懂的地方都可以问我喔。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "真的不记得了喔……？妳们以前关系很好耶。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "嗯……对不起。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "不用道歉啦……从今天开始重新来就好啦！真正关系好的在那边呢～Iris，不过来关心一下 Aroma 吗？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "啊，跑掉了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 B"], "content": "她说要是 Aroma 认不出她，她可能会崩溃。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "哎呀～哪有那么夸张？我外婆之前也有点老人痴呆，后来家里人多陪陪她就没事啦。我去追她。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "什么烂譬喻啊……？那我先好了！ Aroma，还记得我吗？我是 Thomas，我们正在交往喔！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "咦……？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 B"], "content": "喂！你少在那唬烂。 Aroma 我才是妳男朋……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "闪开啦！你们这些臭男生！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos0501"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "哇！不要拉我……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "跟 Aroma 最好的妳不在了还怎么办？搞不好能帮她想起什么耶。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "如何？她是 Iris 喔，妳最好的闺蜜，有印象吗？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……Iris……\nIris……Baker……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "咦！ ？妳记得我！ ？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……呃……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "怎么样！ ？有想到什么吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……对不起，只想得起姓而已……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……呜呜！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 B"], "content": "哭什么啊？太好了啊！再努力一点我们一定可以帮她想起全部的事情的！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "我知道……呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喂喂，别哭了……搞不懂妳是在开心还是伤心。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Iris……我会努力的。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯……呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "对了，说到被遗忘可能会崩溃的家伙，还有一个呢……他应该也能帮 Aroma 想起一些事。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 B"], "content": "对吼，他跟 Clara、Aroma 三大模范生聚在一起一定有帮助……啊，不过他现在八成又在屋顶偷抽烟。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "……我去叫他？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 B"], "content": "算了啦，他今天心情那么差，搞不好会被揍喔？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学 A"], "content": "唉，成绩那么好有什么屁用？他再这样下去操行迟早会被系统扣光。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……哎呀～别管他了啦，我们带 Aroma 去参观学院还比较有用。 Aroma，走吧！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}